      "content": "i know about the lifelines. i've called them. they just give you the same scripted responses. they don't understand. it's not like i'm just \"sad.\" i've spent my whole life building something that doesn't exist. the person i thought i was, the person everyone respected... that person died when the results came back. how am i supposed to just go back to a normal life when my entire identity was built on a lie? there's no \"moving on\" from this. it's just a void now.",
